cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with video/image segmentation and localization, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also leverages two representations at different levels and incorporates a foreground model, which involves machine learning (cs.MM) and optimization (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also uses weakly supervised learning, which is a common theme in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) research. Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed framework on several datasets, which involves information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
